This is a jQuery plugin that makes html tables more flexibles.

* You can truncate cell content if this one is too large for the column width. 
For this, use the option ellipsisClass and add the used class to cells that you want
to be truncated...

$('#table').flextable({
	ellipsisClass: 'truncateme'
});

<table>
	<tr>
		<td class="truncateme">long text</td>
		<td></td>
	</tr>
</table>